;s:11:\"description\";s:189:\"Lounge Lizard brandtenders always serve up original website designs and mobile apps. We mix a potent combination of tasty brand and marketing strategies with a nice splash of street smarts.\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"sort\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"attachment_id\";s:2:\"81\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:72:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/strategy-1-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"image\";s:64:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/strategy-1.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"585\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"535\";}i:1;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"CREATIVE\";s:11:\"description\";s:198:\"Our designers juices are always overflowing. Our creative mixologists stir up innovation with creative artistry, vision, flair and functionality that reflects your Web and Mobile identity and brand.\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"sort\";s:1:\"1\";s:13:\"attachment_id\";s:2:\"82\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:74:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/creative12-2-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"image\";s:66:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/creative12-2.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"585\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"535\";}i:2;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"TECHNOLOGY\";s:11:\"description\";s:229:\"Websites and mobile app technologies are constantly evolving. Our techies are constantly researching and exploring new and innovative ways to develop corporate websites, build mobile apps and shout them out to your target market.\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"sort\";s:1:\"2\";s:13:\"attachment_id\";s:2:\"83\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:75:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/technology2-1-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"image\";s:67:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/technology2-1.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"585\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"535\";}}s:23:\"approach_block_end_text\";s:471:\"Tap into our talented web site designers, graphic artists, content writers, programmers, and digital marketing experts all dedicated to making your brand successful by producing new leads and customers. Our brandtenders hope you’ll choose Lounge Lizard as your new Web Design Company. Here’s our most popular concoctions, web design, web development, company identity, web hosting, search engine marketing, social media management and a splash of website maintenance.\";s:21:\"clients_block_heading\";s:7:\"CLIENTS\";s:18:\"clients_block_text\";s:264:\"SINCE 1998, we’ve designed over 5,000 award-winning web design and website development projects on budget and on-time for over 1,000 start-ups to fortune 100 companies in almost every industry you can think of. Did we mention we have a 99% client retention rate?\";s:19:\"clients_block_boxes\";a:7:{i:0;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:3:\"B2B\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"sort\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"attachment_id\";s:2:\"84\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:72:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/b2b-icon-1-150x150.png\";s:5:\"image\";s:64:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/b2b-icon-1.png\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"220\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"220\";}i:1;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:3:\"B2C\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"sort\";s:1:\"1\";s:13:\"attachment_id\";s:2:\"85\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:72:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/b2c-icon-1-150x150.png\";s:5:\"image\";s:64:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/b2c-icon-1.png\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"220\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"220\";}i:2;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:3:\"CPG\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"sort\";s:1:\"2\";s:13:\"attachment_id\";s:2:\"86\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:72:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CPG-icon-1-150x150.png\";s:5:\"image\";s:64:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/CPG-icon-1.png\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"220\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"220\";}i:3;a:9:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"E-COMMERCE\";s:11:\"description\";s:0:\"\";s:3:\"url\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"sort\";s:1:\"3\";s:13:\"attachment_id\";s:2:\"87\";s:5:\"thumb\";s:76:\"http://localhost/eshop/wp-content/upl